d\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-1/2 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></a></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 relative\"><div class=\"space-y-[50vh] pb-[20vh]\"><div class=\"min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center p-6 rounded-2xl transition-colors duration-500 hover:bg-zinc-900/30 border border-zinc-800/50 hover:border-zinc-800/80 hover:backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check w-6 h-6 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2\">The Paradigm Shift</h3><div class=\"text-blue-500 font-mono text-sm mb-6\">From VDI to Secure Browser</div><p class=\"text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-lg\">传统 VDI 部署成本高、体验差。雪诺方案通过“端+云”架构，将企业办公成本降低 90%。我构建了零信任网关的可视化拓扑逻辑。</p></div><div class=\"min-h-[50vh] flex flex-col justify-center p-6 rounded-2xl transition-colors duration-500 hover:bg-zinc-900/30 border border-zinc-800/50 hover:border-zinc-800/80 hover:backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 